  "text": "Life satisfaction. The five-item Satisfaction with Life Scale [CITATION_1] was utilized to measure respondents' global life satisfaction (␣ ϭ 0.80). Responses were recorded on a scale ranging from 1 (strongly disagree) to 5 (strongly agree). Sample items are, \"In most ways, life is close to ideal,\" \"The conditions of my life are excellent,\" and \"I am satisfied with my life. [CITATION_2] documented evidence supporting the reliability and construct validity of this measure.",
